{'en': {'shortDesc': 'Remote network security auditor, the client', 'pkgName': 'openvas-client', 'longDesc': u'The OpenVAS Security Scanner is a security auditing tool. It makes possible to test security modules in an attempt to find vulnerable spots that should be fixed.\n\nIt is made up of two parts: a server, and a client. The server/daemon, openvasd, is in charge of the attacks, whereas the client, OpenVAS-Client, provides the user a nice X11/GTK+ interface.\n\nThis package contains the GTK+ client.'}}